== 續集及電視劇版 ==
{{main|喪屍樂園：連環屍殺}}

{{link-en|亞馬遜製作公司|Amazon Studios}}投資拍攝了根據2009年同名影片改编的电视剧集《喪屍樂園》，劇情與原片大致相當。由柯克·沃德（Kirk Ward）、{{link-en|泰勒·罗斯|Tyler Ross}}、{{link-en|玛依亚拉·沃尔什|Maiara Walsh}}及伊扎贝拉·维多维奇（Izabela Vidovic）主演。2013年4月19日，美國首播试映集，但观众对此反應並不熱烈，導致僅僅播出一集後，亚马逊网便正式放弃拍攝計劃。劇集的創作人将夭折原因归罪于原版电影爱好者不给面子。<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.digitalspy.com/tv/ustv/news/a482557/zombieland-tv-series-not-picked-up-by-amazon-after-hated-pilot/ |title = 'Zombieland' TV series not picked up by Amazon after "hated" pilot |author = Meg Drewett |date = 2013-05-17 |publisher = Digital Spy |language = en |accessdate = 2016-06-16 |archive-date = 2016-07-10 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160710140648/http://www.digitalspy.com/tv/ustv/news/a482557/zombieland-tv-series-not-picked-up-by-amazon-after-hated-pilot/ |dead-url = no }}</ref>

2016年2月，[[保羅·韋尼克|保羅·韋尼克]]與[[雷特·瑞斯|雷特·瑞斯]]宣佈編寫續集，魯賓·弗來舍也宣佈成為導演。<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.cinemablend.com/new/Zombieland-2-Still-Works-Here-What-We-Know-113797.html |title = Zombieland 2 Is Still In The Works, Here's What We Know |author = Brent Mcknight |publisher = CinemaBlend |language = en |accessdate = 2016-06-16 |archive-date = 2016-06-10 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160610064032/http://www.cinemablend.com/new/Zombieland-2-Still-Works-Here-What-We-Know-113797.html |dead-url = no }}</ref>

續集已在2019年10月11日上映。

